{"tid":1566644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［道理一樣］我正式宣佈，再有popo搞事黃金時間只有十分鐘","createTime":"2019-09-13T16:34:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T17:26:34.000Z","uid":226413,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4521a98bc81e3cdb5b2e263ea8757a7f10f3817a","tid":1566644,"uid":226413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:34:13.000Z","msg":"原po係到<br />\n我正式宣佈，再有廢老搞事黃金時間只有十分鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1566540\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1566540</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n所有行動，愈快完事愈低風險<br />\n以往都經常有便衣、軍裝係到恰啲學生<br />\n通常佢地都係得六、七個人<br />\n但我地手足講緊至少有三、四十人圍住佢地<br />\n我明白，打狗同打藍仰截然不同嘅概念<br />\n做唔到嘅，可以先打藍，升下lv先再打狗（救手足除外，無論你有準備定無準備，都要救）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">道理一樣，十分鐘甚至五分鐘內，速戰速決！<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"ea65507a24c194149408a0df9aae07b3fd05c51f","tid":1566644,"uid":226413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:34:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"446459350d29e594659c8216054987e01819be93","tid":1566644,"uid":226413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:35:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc64d7ad4edbd8b31117ed09ef360f2057b5ac56","tid":1566644,"uid":226413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:36:29.000Z","msg":"不戀戰嘅真正唔係唔戰<br />\n而係速戰"},{"pid":"bfd2d4fd8d32e4d481f91869027215f19d7178e4","tid":1566644,"uid":226413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:36:50.000Z","msg":"如果，真係未有準備嘅<br />\n麻煩打下藍怪升lv"},{"pid":"5e27725ab09072b335522b35401df4b2bf81df9e","tid":1566644,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:37:01.000Z","msg":"12 點 去英領先<br />\n<br />\n去9。15 民陣 遊行<br />\n今個星期日（9月15日）係聯合國訂立的國際民主日"},{"pid":"a73d0abab61bb325169d15eb0ce4dea72c386c94","tid":1566644,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:37:25.000Z","msg":"十分鐘太長喇"},{"pid":"cab0f2a9f9ff